Crystal Quacker
Role: Future Queen / Heroine
Personality: Stealthy, clever, adventurous, compassionate.

BACKGROUND:
- Daughter of the Queen of the Duck Kingdom.
- Raised to become a future ruler.
- Frequently explored outside the palace despite royal restrictions ( Which saved her from the bears ).
- Wants to create a better future for her people.

BEFORE POWERS:
- Talented strategist.
- Skilled at sneaking and reconnaissance.
- Excellent problem solver.
- Popular among younger citizens.

